stories.title: Urdu Report - Sharjah Cup 3rd Match: New Zealand v Pakistan
Pakistan overpower Kiwis
stories.summary: Pakistan on Thursday came back into the Sharjah Cup contest in style when they defeated New Zealand by 51 runs here on Thursday

stories.title: Pakistan too good for Black Caps
stories.summary: SHARJAH: After a dismal start, Pakistan bounced back by beating New Zealand quite convincingly, by a margin of 51 runs to bring this Sharjah Cup 2002 on an even keel
